column5: Can anyone tell me how much ice is still on lac suel as of april 15th,or an approx ice out date...were comin up on the 23 of may ...

I was working off the end of my dock yesterday and there was one foot of ice. It's all honeyconed and this morning where I had a hole two feet square yesterday it is now four feet square. It is forcasted to be 19 degrees centigrade today and 17 tomorrow. Opening week of May will not be an issue this year.
There are large sections of open water in our bay here at gullrock, the ice is getting blacker by the hour.
South Bay across from South Bay on Gullrock Camp.
Red Lake ice out by Friday....
